Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 知世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼啦 一臉吃驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到你真的會來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不是騙子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}外面很冷 先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些全都是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這沒什麼的 畢竟是約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一個人跑出家門好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕才剛過 不會有人誘拐小孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但聖誕當天 你們就被拐走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還以為魔法使的家會更恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想不到又大又乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實她身上有不少小傢伙 還是別說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去書房 你們慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要…要來我的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有香草的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼時候回倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我下個月會再來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也來我家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜歡的話 就帶一點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是點心的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}送禮還回禮 每次見面都像過聖誕節一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很久沒交朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你能教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想做什麼就約我 講出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但如果對方不喜歡的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別人當然和自己不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想做的事也當然不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}語言是為了溝通 不是為了互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸常常這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過討厭的人一開始就討人厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉真是成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明和我差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是如此就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快16了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還想把心裡的話說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但很難做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}練習？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但可不能任性 雖然你不像那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在還希望能趕快去你家玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣算不上是練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那只是預定而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西魯基 他有留下紙條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 能麻煩你送史黛拉回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 你要追上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和那傢伙都不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 史黛拉 下次再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說出心裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的手腳 比嘴巴更會表達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 離他越來越遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我變成能實現應做之事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}狐狸的腳太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}熊的身體太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要跑得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要跑得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有聽到什麼叫聲嗎 狼嚎聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是在找同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次真的變成狼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果剛才吵到你了 我先說聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有沒有哪裡不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是有什麼不順心的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽著你們的聲音 就覺得好想離開家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要史黛拉快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來是想一個人待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是發現你追上來後就冷靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是腳卻停不下來 不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要回去 一起喝下午茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來艾利亞斯這麼不了解自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以為會被他拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許艾利亞斯也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以自戀地認為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是那麼重視著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這麼開心啊 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次什麼時候去奶奶家呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼性急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再出去繞一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們之間的聯繫被干擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在哪裡 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}情況好像有點糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會被他吃掉 被他吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是哪片陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在找你的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們向我的母親貢獻了雨露果實和樹枝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為謝禮 我就把我的火焰借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下個冬天 當我成為母親的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也要給我雨露果實和樹枝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 智世 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 別怕 我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是艾利亞斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 可能是生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}母親以前是怎麼跟我說的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯感覺到的 大概是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}羨慕別人 不知道為什麼只有自己受冷落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但即便羨慕別人 怨恨別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己的痛苦也不會紓解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要把痛苦向別人發洩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要學會自我妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說得好聽 我明明才是最羨慕人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要繼續任性的話 我也有自己的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這一刀下去 我可不知道會刺到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你氣消了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 我已經不生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你剛剛生氣了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家之後好好聊一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聊一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 我們一起聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉今天也教了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也希望艾利亞斯能聽我說說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們可以在被窩裡聊到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前還像父女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在卻像是母子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好 安潔麗卡在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面 我叫大衛‧巴蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是安潔的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 能稍等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您也是魔法使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除了有幸得到工作 又有個和睦的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就沒有優點了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 有客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 最近她心情有點不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊 我最近也碰到過類似的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大衛 你剛才叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩滋華斯昏睡不醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 從26號晚上開始一直沒醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很睏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一朵 兩朵 何處開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}窗邊孩兒就要入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}淡淡月光襯白花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三朵 四朵 何處開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽的鏡子鑲花邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青青花兒偷綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唱了搖籃曲後就睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己也查了很久 但還是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說歸說 你還不是試了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要對艾利亞斯保密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果是歌聲混入了魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那歌聲就成了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般來說只有有意為之才會變成魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這也許是你的特殊能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那為什麼我不擅長做安眠藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你給的手鐲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次聖誕我會回禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我就好好期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用了 謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體不舒服的話 先躺一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說你經常勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是去醫院就能治好的病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最好不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定有人把你說得跟親女兒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔一直是我們邂逅時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從我還是毛頭小鬼開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花了兩隻手都數不完的歲月追求她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才得到了她的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等女兒出生後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近我才知道她為何一直不肯點頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很幸福 不會一個人離開人世的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過安潔 還有我們的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們只能看著別人離開 卻不知自己的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一想到還能歡聲笑語到什麼時候 就很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你和我不一樣 運氣好就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我們都不要勉強自己 莽莽撞撞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}儘可能活久一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 要幫忙嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是藥催醒的 還是那一拳頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑到這麼遠的地方會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是小孩子走太遠很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊有東西在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是你們 密獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愚蠢的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是管理者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖乖粉身碎骨吧
